name: LabNotebook
body:
A no-frills Lab Notebook for EECS 399, Senior Project.
Features include:
Importing of images
Encryption  
PDF Support 

Library Dependencies:
SHEF WYSIWYG Editor  ( http://shef.sourceforge.net/ )
Apache Commons Codec 1.9 (http://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-codec/)
ICEpdf 5.04 (http://www.icesoft.org/java/projects/ICEpdf/overview.jsf)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
